1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 12=

21
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,680
Your Majesty.

22
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:34,200
Whose palace

23
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:36,510
will you rest in tonight?

24
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,640
I'll go speak with Noble Lady Hui.

25
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,790
Your Majesty,

26
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,560
Noble Lady Hui has

27
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,480
was grounded by the Dowager.

28
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,320
Confined?

29
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:45,760
Why?

30
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:48,120
For breaking palace rules.

31
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:51,070
The Dowager didn't give details.

32
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,760
Your Majesty,

33
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,200
Consort Lan

34
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,710
sent Biqing with soup again.

35
00:01:58,710 --> 00:02:02,230
It's been ten days since you visited her.

36
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,430
Fine.

37
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,120
Let's head to her palace.

38
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,150
Yes.

39
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,640
Biqing.

40
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,240
Is there something else?

41
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,840
Your Majesty.

42
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:36,710
Your Majesty.

43
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,590
What brings you here?

44
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,710
Biqing did not even announce.

45
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,590
I told her not to.

46
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:44,750
I

47
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,000
wanted to surprise you.

48
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,840
A surprise?

49
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,120
More like a scare.

50
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:54,800
You've ignored me for so long.

51
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:56,430
I thought you forgot

52
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,240
where I lived.

53
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,120
Visiting so late.

54
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,280
Which girl

55
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:05,630
kicked you out?

56
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,470
If that's how you feel,

57
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,960
then I won't stay.

58
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,190
I'll head back to the hall.

59
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,750
Since you're here,

60
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,520
don't think I'm letting you go.

61
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,710
I've been buried in work lately.

62
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,680
Reviewing reports every day

63
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,000
is exhausting.

64
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,910
I finally had a free moment.

65
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,470
I realized

66
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,080
I hadn't seen you.

67
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,800
I missed you.

68
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,190
I thought

69
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:43,400
some newcomer stole your heart.

70
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:46,240
And you forgot what I looked like.

71
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,520
I could never

72
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,430
forget you.

73
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,520
You're my Consort Lan.

74
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,280
Nobody can replace you.

75
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,080
You have a smooth tongue.

76
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,630
It's late.

77
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,360
Come to bed.

78
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,000
Zhen'er.

79
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:24,000
Why are you here at this hour?

80
00:04:24,550 --> 00:04:25,390
Biqing.

81
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,230
It's me.

82
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,120
Is His Majesty here?

83
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:29,870
I have urgent news to report.

84
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,160
It concerns life and death.

85
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,480
They're resting.

86
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,720
Have you forgotten the rules?

87
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,480
Disturbing the Emperor at nigh

88
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,390
is a crime.

89
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:39,390
But...

90
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,630
Consort Duan's having

91
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:41,800
terrible abdominal pain.

92
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,390
That old trick again?

93
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,390
Abdominal pain?

94
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,430
Go get a physician.

95
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,920
What can the Emperor do?

96
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,190
What are you waiting for?

97
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,510
Take her back.

98
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:55,800
Your Majesty. Please see Consort Duan.

99
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:57,430
She's in pain.

100
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:58,480
- His Majesty.
- Silence.

101
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,430
If you disturb,

102
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,270
you're dead.

103
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,070
What's all the noise?

104
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:06,750
Your Majesty,

105
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,800
it's Zhen'er from Consort Duan's palace.

106
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,360
She's crying to see you.

107
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,630
Says the Consort is unwell.

108
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:13,870
It might be serious.

109
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:16,920
His Majesty,

110
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:18,870
servants always exaggerate.

111
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,920
Her words may not be true.

112
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,190
Besides, the physicians are there.

113
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,040
Consort Duan is with child.

114
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,240
I should go check on her.

115
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,720
My love, go to bed.

116
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,040
I'll be back soon.

117
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,590
Your Highness.

118
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,870
It's all Zhen'er's fault.

119
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,270
I couldn't stop her.

120
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,960
Your Majesty.

121
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,480
I heard you were feeling unwell.

122
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,800
I came to check on you.

123
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,120
Did you call a physician?

124
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,310
I'm okay.

125
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,630
The pregnancy is just unstable.

126
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,430
I'm sorry

127
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,240
to disturb you.

128
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,000
You are with child.

129
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,120
Just focus on resting.

130
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,400
Don't worry

131
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,070
about anything else.

132
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,720
Your Majesty has worked hard.

133
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,240
I prepared a bowl of lotus seed soup.

134
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,390
I shelled the lotus seeds myself.

135
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,040
It's been just a few days,

136
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,120
and you have

137
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,630
a new maid?

138
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,310
Your Majesty.

139
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:24,270
I'm Liu Mei, from the side chamber.

140
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,310
If that's the case,

141
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,510
why are you here at night?

142
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,630
Didn't they teach you the rules?

143
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:34,310
Your Majesty.

144
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,240
I asked her to stay.

145
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,160
At present,

146
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,240
I'm preserving my pregnancy.

147
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:44,510
I can hardly attend myself.

148
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:48,190
Liu Mei serves in my palace.

149
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:52,480
She's well-mannered and sweet.

150
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,040
And if

151
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,630
you don't mind,

152
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:59,920
let her serve you in the side chamber.

153
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,160
Consider it

154
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:04,480
a favor to me.

155
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,960
You're truly

156
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,560
very thoughtful.

157
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,560
Greetings, Consort Duan.

158
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,920
Where is His Majesty?

159
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,440
He left?

160
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,790
Your Highness.

161
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,200
He left before dawn.

162
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,390
Eunuch Sixi was with him.

163
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,600
He didn't say much.

164
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,510
Did he give you a reward?

165
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,270
Or a promotion?

166
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,270
No.

167
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,790
I offered to help him dress.

168
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,080
He told me not to bother.

169
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,390
He said I should go back to sleep.

170
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,120
I didn't want to disturb him.

171
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,030
You really are

172
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,670
too sincere and endearing.

173
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,080
He said "don't bother,"

174
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,320
and you simply

175
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:08,200
went back to rest?

176
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,510
You need to be more assertive.

177
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:15,000
Let him feel your affection

178
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,390
and attachment to him.

179
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,240
Otherwise,

180
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,480
how would he remember you?

181
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,840
Then…

182
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,720
I…

183
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,800
Fine.

184
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,630
I'll help you one more time.

185
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,440
I'll secure a rank for you.

186
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,270
All right?

187
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,600
Now,

188
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,270
you live in my side chamber

189
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,870
and have attend the Emperor.

190
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,750
You deserve to be a First Attendant.

191
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,440
That's only right.

192
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:49,480
Thank you, Your Highness.

193
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:52,790
I am yours to command.

194
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:55,360
I'll do anything for you.

195
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,840
As long as you know

196
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,840
where you stand

197
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,000
and who helped you get there.

198
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,960
I won't let you down.

199
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,790
She's just attended once.

200
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,960
Is that rank a bit too high?

201
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:37,360
The harem splits in two.

202
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,240
I've been

203
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:43,000
standing sworn against Consort Lan.

204
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,630
Now,

205
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,000
with the unborn heir,

206
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,600
the inner court

207
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:54,000
belongs to me alone.

208
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,150
This time,

209
00:10:57,790 --> 00:11:00,600
I want the new girls

210
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,960
to see clearly

211
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:04,670
who truly

212
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:08,000
runs this palace.

213
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:19,120
By Imperial Decree,

214
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,360
Second Attendant of the Qijia clan

215
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,000
is virtuous and prudent,

216
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,750
diligent and compliant.

217
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:26,870
You are hereby promoted to First Attendant.

218
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,670
Respect this decree.

219
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:31,000
I thank His Majesty for this grace.

220
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,390
Congratulations, First Attendant Liu.

221
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,270
Please, for your trouble.

222
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,150
Uh...

223
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,790
Oh, I couldn't.

224
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:43,510
Well, congrats again.

225
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:02,320
Well played, Consort Duan.

226
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:05,550
To dare act right under my nose

227
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:08,200
with a feint in the open,

228
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:10,320
while striking in secret.

229
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,390
Now Liu Mei's been made First Attendant.

230
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:17,200
Grateful to Consort Duan for raising her up,

231
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,790
she obeys her every command.

232
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,870
Duan is using this to recruit the others.

233
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,150
The new girls

234
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,720
are already following her.

235
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:25,960
If this goes on,

236
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,150
the power balance will shift.

237
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,960
All these years, Lady Fucha

238
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,960
has hidden behind that gentle face of hers.

239
00:12:34,390 --> 00:12:36,150
She's a good actress.

240
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,960
She can't win on favor

241
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,670
or power.

242
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:42,360
So she uses her pregnancy

243
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:45,320
to climb higher.

244
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,750
Perhaps

245
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:50,670
we should offer some boons.

246
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:53,200
They need an incentive

247
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,960
to stay in line.

248
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,480
Now that she's pregnant,

249
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,790
she can't serve.

250
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:01,790
Someone else must do it in her stead.

251
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,240
But why should I

252
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,670
just give his favor away?

253
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,960
Her pregnancy

254
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,870
has a long way to go.

255
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,390
I'll make sure

256
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,790
she pays for this.

257
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,200
Yes.

258
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,560
Hui.

259
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,320
You've been grounded for days.

260
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,200
I'm sure

261
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,870
the kitchen hasn't been kind.

262
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:46,240
So I borrowed some snacks

263
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,510
from the Dowager.

264
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,550
Consider it a gift from her.

265
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,720
I'm glad you remembered me.

266
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,550
Copying these scriptures

267
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:55,200
made me hungry.

268
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,200
Try it.

269
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:03,350
Is it good?

270
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,550
Seeing how calm you are,

271
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:10,270
I can finally rest easy.

272
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,720
It's just a timeout.

273
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,270
If I lose my composure,

274
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,750
I fall right into their trap.

275
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,390
Well said.

276
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:21,080
I did some digging for you.

277
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:23,440
Before the Dowager scolded you,

278
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:26,270
a young eunuch was
stirring up trouble before her.

279
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:27,750
That young eunuch

280
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:31,150
belongs to Consort Lan.

281
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:33,870
So it really was her.

282
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:34,710
Mm.

283
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:38,750
A clever way to use someone else's hands.

284
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,800
Mm.

285
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:41,550
One more thing.

286
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:42,670
These past few days,

287
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,480
His Majesty has newly bestowed a title

288
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:45,720
on a First Attendant.

289
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,120
It is Liu Mei.

290
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:49,630
She's Consort Duan's girl now.

291
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,030
Just as your thunder fades,

292
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:54,080
she brings in a newcomer.

293
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,840
Consort Duan

294
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,600
doesn't want you to have a comeback.

295
